WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.070 --> 00:00:02.995
Easy Workspace brings pending changes

2
00:00:03.015 --> 00:00:05.245
into one clear review list.

3
00:00:05.265 --> 00:00:07.050
An editor opens the paper-plane

4
00:00:07.070 --> 00:00:08.815
menu, sees related pages and

5
00:00:08.835 --> 00:00:11.835
content elements, and deselects anything

6
00:00:11.855 --> 00:00:13.295
that is not ready.

7
00:00:13.315 --> 00:00:15.135
TYPO3 then publishes only the

8
00:00:15.155 --> 00:00:17.440
selected records, placing parent records

9
00:00:17.460 --> 00:00:18.745
before their children.

10
00:00:18.765 --> 00:00:21.065
This makes partial releases easier

11
00:00:21.085 --> 00:00:22.760
to understand and control.

12
00:00:22.780 --> 00:00:24.225
The feature page shows the

13
00:00:24.245 --> 00:00:25.690
review and publishing flow.
